    "body": "The test may fail intermittently when the `net` thread is lagging while calling `DeleteNode`. This may result in a split `getdata`, meaning that `peer2.wait_for_parent_requests([int(parent_peekaboo_AB[\"txid\"], 16), int(parent_missing[\"txid\"], 16)])` fails.\r\n\r\nFix it by adding a sync on the `net` thread.\r\n\r\nFixes #31700",
